    "visualization_explanation": "The dataset contains 3 categorical series (medal types) across 5 ordinal categories (countries). Synthetic medal counts follow realistic Olympic distributions with Norway leading (\u03bc=132 gold medals, \u03c3=25.8). The polar projection emphasizes cyclical comparisons while inversion improves label readability. Stacked columns maximize data-ink ratio by encoding totals through bar height and composition through color segments. Pattern fills with national flag sprites implement Cairo's pre-attentive processing principles for immediate category recognition. Value labels use D3-style formatting consistency (+/- 1 medal precision) while maintaining accessibility through keyboard-navigable series elements."
